column10:
"Definitive Edition" who is way worse than the original edition.

The complete cursed package:

-Several graphical glitchs in the city;
-Pathetic graphical glitchs in cutscenes;
-Framerate Drops;
-Various audio bugs;
-A new list of minors bugs and glitchs;
-Visuals now have a strange dark looking and a ugly palette of colors;

Characters received a "facelift" that looked strange and too dark, with an artificial appearance.

Excellent game really but dog sh!t dlcs...
You f*cking need to drive 1000 miles in Jimmy dlc for 100% the achievements pls wtf ?!
 except Joe's one (comeback of playboy magazines)
